3.3 Finding an initial basic feasible solution
Let us consider \text{LP.Canonical}.

\begin{align*}
&\min_{x \in \mathbb{R}^n} c^{\top}x \\
\text{s.t. } & Ax = b\\
& x_i \geq 0, \; i = 1,\dots, n
